36
00:02:43,862 --> 00:02:45,163
and I could smile.

37
00:02:46,193 --> 00:02:47,262
But...

38
00:02:53,503 --> 00:02:56,743
Chung Ah...

39
00:03:03,042 --> 00:03:05,783
(Mom, I like you.)

40
