94
00:09:48,883 --> 00:09:50,552
(Contact us to join the band, First Love Memory Manipulators.)

95
00:09:51,353 --> 00:09:53,253
I didn't react like that because I disliked you.

96
00:09:53,952 --> 00:09:55,062
The truth is...

97
00:10:01,633 --> 00:10:03,503
I wanted to thank you.

98
00:10:08,942 --> 00:10:13,243
I wanted to thank you for helping me and finding me.

99
00:10:13,743 --> 00:10:15,383
That's why I went to see you.

100
00:10:15,812 --> 00:10:18,082
To show you how I really felt.

101
00:10:18,253 --> 00:10:19,253
But...

102
00:10:21,283 --> 00:10:24,123
